    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>capers </strong>roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped capers</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>mayo</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Squeeze in the <strong>juice</strong> of<strong> 1</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]<strong> </span>lemon wedge<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tartare sauce</strong></p>",
